  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Preparedness and Response Intervention for COVID-19 to Reduce Associated Morbidity and Mortality in Displacement Settings in Eastern Democratic Republic of the Congo</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">IOM provides handwashing kits and awareness raising through risk communication and community engagement related to COVID-19 prevention to conflict affected population residing in 61 displacement sites across North Kivu, Tanganyika and Ituri provinces. IOM continues to support the provision of site management and site administration services in 61 displacement sites and will provide water and sanitation health services.</narrative>
  </description>
